{"tid":1927194,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"喺呢個時候唔應該理廿三條","createTime":"2020-03-15T15:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:08:27.000Z","uid":131767,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da288a38ee200b5738b275900adfe863e0e9732b","tid":1927194,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">支那點解呢個時候搞廿三條?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有一個目的，就係分散香港人抗爭目標</span></span><br />\n好簡單例子<br />\n支那傳播武漢肺炎之後<br />\n香港人忙住叫政府封關，忙住揾口罩物資<br />\n就住真雙普選嘅努力自然大量減少<br />\n又真雙普選又功能組別又要防武漢肺炎<br />\n香港人就得咁多，做得幾多樣嘢?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">噉點解唔應該理廿三條?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為只要你至少撐《香港人權及民主法》<br />\n或者撐進攻功能組別其中一樣<br />\n都唔需要理對家搞廿三條</span></span><br />\n<br />\n撐plan a《香港人權及民主法》嘅<br />\n今年內只有制裁or普選俾支那揀<br />\n已經係第一重將軍<br />\n<br />\n撐plan b進攻功能組別嘅<br />\n照進攻功能組別支持者嘅理論<br />\n立法會過半就贏到<br />\n係重炮將<br />\n<br />\n關心廿三條只係會將香港人注意力分散<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>只要有真雙普選<br />\n廿三條問題自然會消失<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"06d571b5d2e3ba882eda275bcf5061c99891947d","tid":1927194,"uid":131767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"TLDR：<br />\n求下大家咪撚理班戇鳩保皇啊<br />\n咁得閒就關心國際戰線(plan a)<br />\n問下人登記咗選民未啦(plan b)"},{"pid":"e4f20b932d619e1ee3a165f098c2650d2da0e5d8","tid":1927194,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T15:57:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd62c1218b2065fd158c7ee7035045004ef3955e","tid":1927194,"uid":306914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔係掉返轉，用廿三條再加強形聚力，用D口號例如呢頭撤送中，嗰頭本地送你終去形容廿三條？"},{"pid":"dc13249d3f2b690a6a89d0e573a0dee402f9f239","tid":1927194,"uid":343189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd62c1218b2065fd158c7ee7035045004ef3955e","tid":1927194,"uid":306914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔係掉返轉，用廿三條再加強形聚力，用D口號例如呢頭撤送中，嗰頭本地送你終去形容廿三條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"因為佢地唔想市民反對23條囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1306a2699c941fdc1a4630392a25e200041c3744","tid":1927194,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd62c1218b2065fd158c7ee7035045004ef3955e","tid":1927194,"uid":306914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔係掉返轉，用廿三條再加強形聚力，用D口號例如呢頭撤送中，嗰頭本地送你終去形容廿三條？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"簡單嚟講<br />\n港共根本未出聲(但知情，亦支持搞呢場大龍鳳)<br />\n成個廿三條其實係假議題<br />\n正如藍屍嘅KOL100行動<br />\n成班無人識嘅二打六<br />\n你唔理佢哋，佢哋就一事無成<br />\n你愈理佢哋佢哋就愈紅<br />\nKOL100呢個行動先會成功<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ot7KxZS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fot7KxZS.png&h=c4b42a8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ff7728af4d8c2f2d23c94be6f4ddc9dd0683161","tid":1927194,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc13249d3f2b690a6a89d0e573a0dee402f9f239","tid":1927194,"uid":343189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd62c1218b2065fd158c7ee7035045004ef3955e","tid":1927194,"uid":306914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔係掉返轉，用廿三條再加強形聚力，用D口號例如呢頭撤送中，嗰頭本地送你終去形容廿三條？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"因為佢地唔想市民反對23條囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"而家捉緊五子棋<br />\n黃色棋已經連成四子<br />\n頭(Plan a)尾(Plan b)都叫糊 <br />\n藍色棋見無路可守 <br />\n索性自己都連成四子 <br />\n呢個情況你會揀頭揀尾，定揀防守?"},{"pid":"c45fed82e516aea71f33649df73828e23de0f9fc","tid":1927194,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家最緊重要選民登記"},{"pid":"459d70d4edb8f4d1f613c5f07ad3a175cf53d967","tid":1927194,"uid":159309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"然後通過埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0a78c873fca339bdfb254a8371442a868b2d5e","tid":1927194,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"唔理佢然後過左你乜戰線都唔使搞，因為你呢個post已經足夠令你比人拉"},{"pid":"76e212d6e84fd4407710d6b34d52de0a7966e2c5","tid":1927194,"uid":131767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a78c873fca339bdfb254a8371442a868b2d5e","tid":1927194,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"唔理佢然後過左你乜戰線都唔使搞，因為你呢個post已經足夠令你比人拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"搞笑，講到而家無鳩拉人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點係香港法治一早死咗</strong></span><br />\n黑警要拉要姦要殺無後果<br />\n淋病要立惡法用緊急法就得<br />\n無法治下佢加幾多條惡法都係一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n明明有暴動可以告人<br />\n點解仲要多鳩餘立個禁幪面法啊？<br />\n因為要你哋將抗爭目標轉移去反禁幪面法<br />\n<br />\n點解派何已完呢啲二打六出嚟爭取廿三條<br />\n唔派傳統保皇黨啊？<br />\n因為要將呢個假議題拉長嚟玩<br />\n最好立法會完咗都未搞掂<br />\n中間再嚟個禁幪面法上訴得直<br />\n又真雙普選又立法會又抗武漢肺炎又禁幪面法又廿三條<br />\n一堆假支線消耗哂香港人嘅抗爭力量<br />\n到時就真係乜都唔洗搞"}]}